      "content": "it's more than just \"instability\" though. it's like the system needs to be reminded that it's not perfect. if everything just runs smoothly forever, it gets stagnant and predictable. people start thinking the tech is infallible. i feel like i'm providing a necessary service to the digital ecosystem by forcing these little stresses. don't you think the web needs a bit of a shakeup every now and then to stay healthy?",
